metadata.description: App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.
App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.
This App uses SSL certificate pinning to detect or  prevent MITM attacks in secure communication channel.
App can write to App Directory. Sensitive Information should be encrypted.

- **Antibiotics (like tetracyclines):** Reduces absorption; take them hours apart.
- **Diuretics:** Can deplete magnesium levels over time.
- **Proton Pump Inhibitors (PPIs):** Long-term use can lower magnesium absorption."

"str_nutrient_detail_desc4_omega3" : "Omega-3 fats shine when combined with:

- **Best Forms:** Magnesium citrate (good absorption), glycinate (gentle on the stomach), or oxide (less expensive but lower absorption).
- **Dosage:** Adults need 310–420 mg/day. Be cautious of high doses, as they can cause diarrhea."

Naturally found in fruits, vegetables, and dairy, it’s also added to many processed foods for flavor. While small amounts of natural sugar are beneficial, excessive added sugar can lead to health problems."

"str_nutrient_detail_desc4_protein" : "Protein pairs best with:

- **Healthy Fats:** Improve digestion and absorption of nutrients. ������

- **Unsaturated Fats:** Healthy fats found in nuts, seeds, and oils.
- **Saturated Fats:** Found in animal products, better consumed in moderation.
- **Trans Fats:** Artificially created fats, which should be avoided."

Calorie Recommendations

Our calorie recommendations are calculated using the Mifflin-St Jeor equation, which is recognized for its accuracy in determining Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR). By considering your BMR, activity level, and specific goals, we provide a customized daily calorie intake suggestion that aligns with your health objectives.

- Men: BMR = 10 x weight (kg) + 6.25 x height (cm) - 5 x age (years) + 5  

- Women: BMR = 10 x weight (kg) + 6.25 x height (cm) - 5 x age (years) - 161  

We advocate for a gradual and sustainable pace for weight loss or gain, with a maximum of 1 kg (2.2 lb) per week.

playstore_details.title: Calorie Counter・Planner・DietAI
playstore_details.description:
New Year, New You! Start tracking calories in 2025 with a 70% Discount!

Kickstart your health journey with our "New Year, New You" campaign! For a limited time, enjoy 70% off DietAI Premium: our biggest discount so far! Crush your New Year's resolutions with advanced tools to help you lose weight, eat healthier, and achieve your wellness goals. Don’t wait, start transforming your health today!

DietAI is your all-in-one calorie counter and nutrition tracker designed to help you achieve your health and fitness goals. Whether you're aiming for weight loss, muscle gain, or maintaining a healthy lifestyle, DietAI provides personalized diet plans tailored to your specific needs. Track your calories, macros, and nutrients effortlessly with our AI-powered food diary and meal planner.

🌟 Personalized Diet Plans and Meal Tracking

Custom Diets: Choose from a variety of diets such as Keto, Intermittent Fasting, Mediterranean, High Protein, Low Carb, Anti-Inflammatory, DASH, and Diabetic diets.
Tailored Recommendations: The app creates custom plans based on your fitness profile, including your height, weight, allergies, and target weight.
Weight Loss Goals: Set your goals and let DietAI guide you on your weight loss journey with structured meal plans and calorie deficit strategies.

🤖 AI Photo & Text Meal Logging

Effortless Logging: Simplify meal tracking with AI-powered features that allow you to log your meals by taking a photo or providing a brief description.
Instant Calculations: The app instantly calculates macronutrients, calories, and essential nutrients like potassium, iron, and magnesium.
Food Scanner: Quickly scan food photos to automatically fetch nutritional information and add items to your food diary.

📊 Comprehensive Nutrition and Macro Tracking

Macro Tracker: Monitor your intake of carbs, proteins, fats, and over 25 essential nutrients like vitamins and minerals.
Nutrition Insights: Get in-depth nutrient analysis to help you stay on top of your nutritional goals, whether you're tracking high protein foods, low-calorie snacks, or high fiber foods.
Custom Targets: Set personalized goals for macros, calories, and nutrients to align with your diet plan.

🏃 Fitness and Activity Integration

Exercise Tracking: Log workouts and daily activities to see their impact on your calorie and nutrient needs.
Progress Monitoring: Track your weight over time with interactive graphs.

🧬 In-Depth Nutrient Analysis

Balanced Diet Support: Whether you're following a pescatarian, vegetarian, carnivore, or any other diet, DietAI ensures you maintain a balanced intake of key vitamins and minerals.
Essential Nutrients: Keep track of nutrients like vitamin D, iron, magnesium, and more to support your overall health.

💡 Personal AI Dietitian and Expert Guidance

Customized Advice: With a personal AI dietitian at your fingertips, get expert recommendations tailored to your goals.
Weight Loss Programs: Get information about structured meal plans, calorie deficit strategies, and weight watcher techniques to accelerate your progress.
Health Tips: Receive guidance on the best ways to lose belly fat, boost metabolism, and find effective fat burners with AI dietitian.

🍽️ Healthy Meal and Snack Suggestions

Meal Planner: Discover healthy meals for dinner, high protein snacks, low-calorie snacks, and more that fit your diet plan.
Diet-Friendly Foods: Find ketosis-friendly foods, anti-inflammatory foods, and high fiber options to support your health.
Recipe Ideas: Explore a variety of recipes tailored to your dietary preferences and nutritional needs with Dietitian AI.
